    "Conv1D and DNN deep learning models, on the other hand, achieved lower accuracy and F1-score values, with Conv1D at 53.64% and 38.60% and DNN at 54.10% and 38.10%, respectively.",
    "However, when the augmented dataset is used, there is a significant improvement in model performance across the board.",
    "RF, MLP, and XGB models have significantly improved accuracy, precision, recall, and F1-score.",
    "MLP and XGB achieved astounding accuracy levels of 95.65% and 95.31%, respectively, with precision, recall, and F1-score values over 96%.",
    "Random Forest achieved an accuracy of 80.92% with precision, recall, and F1-score values that were balanced at around 81.89%."
